er wieder neu aus verschiedenen Perspektiven imaginiert und konstruiert wird.  afunded by Hessische Kulturstiftung  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 0aCulture. 4aDeutschland. 4aFrankfurt Am Main. 4aInterkulturalität. 4aIntermedialität. 4aKultur. 4aKultursoziologie. 4aKünstlerische Forschung. 4aMigration. 4aPostkolonialismus. 4aRelationale Soziologie. 4aRelationale Ästhetik. 4aSoziologie. 4aSüdamerika. 4aTranskulturalität. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Emigration & Immigration.2bisacsh  aArtistic Research.  aCulture.  aFrankfurt Am Main.  aGermany.  aInterculturalism.  aIntermediality.  aMigration.  aPostcolonialism.  aSociology of Culture.  aSociology.  aSouth America.  aTransculturality.2 aHessische Kulturstiftungefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2019z978311071956708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2019z9783110606485oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.14361/9783839448946zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839448946423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783839448946.jpg  a978-3-11-071956-7  DG Plus eBook-Package 2019b2019  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2019  aZDB-23-DSWb2019